{{right| 
[[File:Takenouchi-Touge01.JPG|thumb|none|256px|{{ill|Takenouchi Pass|ja|竹内峠|12=draft|12=draft}} (at the Osaka-Nara prefectural border). The left side is part of {{ill|National Route 166|ja|国道166号|1=Japan National Route 166|12=draft|12=draft}}, while the right side shows the old highway.]]
